data.description: Beautifully kept home situated in a serene rural subdivision, conveniently close to the Air Force Base yet within reach of vibrant surroundings! Just a stone's throw from Tolleson Elementary School, offering effortless access to both the base and the freeway. This residence features clean living with new solar,  exquisite custom wood cabinets, elegant granite countertops, top-tier Frigidaire Professional appliances, engineered hardwood floors complemented by tiled wet areas, a spacious patio, a new AC unit installed in 2022, and an accompanying 10x12 portable building. Don't delay—this stunning home is a must-see!
